metadata. Read the playbook below and respond with ONLY a single JSON object
matching this exact schema:

{
  "description": "one line, imperative — what this playbook sets up/does",
  "category": "a coarse classification, e.g. \"Android / build\"",
  "tags": ["keyword", ...],
  "importantEnvVars": [
    { "name": "ENV_VAR_NAME", "why": "one-line reason this var matters to THIS playbook" }
