Field rules:
- description: ONE line, imperative voice.
- category: a short classification string (e.g. "Android / build").
- tags: an array of short keyword strings.
- importantEnvVars: an array of {name, why} objects for the environment
  variables important to THIS playbook — each the var NAME and a one-line WHY
  it matters. Include vars that matter even if they are not textually in a
  code block. Do NOT include any value; do NOT invent vars. Empty array if none.

Respond with the JSON object ONLY: no prose, no explanation, no markdown code
fence — just the raw JSON.

